text:
Quaint Village that houses NTUC  Supermarket as well as SHENG SIONG
Supermarket that link to Happy Coffee Shop ☕️ [ that serves the sumptuous local Cusines: Koo Kee Noodles,  Cai Png,
Hainanese Chicken 🐔  Rice,  Bak Choy Mee,
Roti Prata,  Nasi Lemak /Padang.
It has Wellness Centres: Foot/ Shoulder/
Body 💆‍♀️ 💆‍♂️  Massages, Clinics, Sze
Chuan Restaurant as well as MacDonalds
in the Village.

Finally have a proper laundromat here! BLK 740
Leave my clothes for a 30min wash while I go for a jog 😂

Nicely surprised by the quality of this park. The trail is great and it loops 4.3km around the Bedok reservoir. It is a great place to run or do exercise.
The car park is not big, but it is close to the Bedok reservoir MRT.
By chance tried the double boiled soup at the coffee shop. It's surprisingly nice and good value! Stall owner is friendly too.

Shengsiong n ntuc is there to get ur groceries also many eateries around so u can relax have a bite n if possible have  ur hair done or just relax by the reservoir .it's a peaceful place.i moved nearby to Bedok Reservoir cos  it's a quiet place to retire to.
